    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age both inside and out. Mechanically, it starts and runs consistently, but you may notice some minor fluid seeps and a suspension that feels less firm than it once was. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, small dings, and some fading paint on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. It is a solid choice for someone needing dependable transportation who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection or minor upcoming maintenance needs.",
